net.openhft.chronicle.network.connection

Class SocketAddressSupplier

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.openhft.chronicle.network.connection.SocketAddressSupplier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Supplier<SocketAddress>

    public class SocketAddressSupplier
extends Object
implements Supplier<SocketAddress>
    Provides support for the client to failover TCP connections to different servers, if the primary connection can not be establish, after retrying up to a timeout, see timeoutMS() the other connections will be attempted. The order of these connections are determined by the order of the connectURIs
    Author:
    Rob Austin.
